            <Insight title="Engagement Analysis" accent={P.mint} icon={Ic.pulse(P.mint,16)}>Facebook has generated <strong>{fmt(computed.fb.clicks)} clicks</strong> at <strong>{fR(computed.fb.cpc)} CPC</strong> with {pc(computed.fb.ctr)} CTR, confirming strong creative-audience alignment on the platform. Instagram contributed {fmt(computed.ig.clicks)} clicks at {fR(computed.ig.cpc)} CPC with {pc(computed.ig.ctr)} CTR. The combined Meta engagement of <strong>{fmt(m.clicks)} clicks</strong> at {fR(m.cpc)} blended CPC represents efficient conversion of awareness into measurable intent signals. TikTok contributed {fmt(t.clicks)} clicks through its performance network, with engagement metrics carrying additional amplification value as TikTok\u2019s algorithm promotes content with strong interaction signals. {m.cpc<2?"Meta CPC below R2.00 is a positive efficiency signal \u2014 consider scaling budget on top-performing ad sets.":m.cpc>5?"Meta CPC above R5.00 warrants creative review and potential audience refresh.":""}</Insight>
